{"type": "article", "id": 22818, "title": "灯光杯", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-25T07:36:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 117, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144116s1Fad2mANHGQDfj0.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是韩国设计师 Jin-woog Koo 和 Bo-hyung Kim 一起设计的灯光杯，灵感源于韩国一种传统的风景画。杯子是反扣在盘子里的，杯子里的 LED 光源透过杯子上的凹凸纹路将灯光按照明暗深浅分层，似乎能看到日月和云海，很有意境。而当放在盘子上时又能作为水杯使用。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144113hVvlmjp7Xy1QWaud.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.69559902\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144114GEFQ6XRkI0Z2Coxc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.29828851\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144114UZmqSKoDtPNkAhOl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144115YKyxErfbp5VBl9eh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.97677262\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n"}